alerts.description:
There is a risk of light snowfall (Level 1 of 4).
Precipitation amounts: < 1 cm

There is a risk of frost (Level 1 of 2).
Minimum temperature: ~ -1 °C

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Height range: > 600 m; Max. gusts: < 60 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then north-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 70 km/h

There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 70-80 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then north-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 90 km/h
There is a risk of icy surfaces (Level 1 of 4).

There is a risk of frost (Level 1 of 2).
Minimum temperature: -2 - -7 °C; local minimum: in valleys and dips > -9 °C
